{"tid":2019692,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米CEO雷軍用 iPhone 發微博令小粉紅崩潰 為解畫竟爆其他支那手機廠高層 全用iPhone：因是最好的智能手機","createTime":"2020-05-16T12:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T03:26:52.000Z","uid":28114,"like":61,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"6ac0055f38ac7e10cf0ec3797eb44dadf8f30900","tid":2019692,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:52:11.000Z","msg":"雷軍用 iPhone 發微博   小米高層「借刀」爆他人私隱<br />\n<br />\n如果有人見到 Tim Cook 使用華為手機，可能是科技界的大新聞，同樣地，小米 CEO 雷軍日前以 iPhone 發出了一條微博，同樣引來了大陸網民的熱甩討論。有網民認為雷軍作為小米手機的最大代言人，不應該使用其他品牌的手機，無法接受他公開使用 iPhone。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2020-05/13/215827/uniqlo_1_d88f0fe68604f035d5efb032fa59396b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2020-05%2F13%2F215827%2Funiqlo_1_d88f0fe68604f035d5efb032fa59396b.jpg&h=8dcf45ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事緣雷軍打算在微博分享自己買了幾本書，並上載了相片，有眼利的網友發現這條微博是以 iPhone 發出，及後雷軍將原本的貼文刪除，利用小米 10 Pro 再發一次。為了協助雷軍解圍，小米高層兼合夥人潘九堂竟然在微博，借助他人之手爆其他手機品牌高層的私隱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2020-05/13/215827/uniqlo_1_3d8eb0d37182bb3f46c58dc93ed06be9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2020-05%2F13%2F215827%2Funiqlo_1_3d8eb0d37182bb3f46c58dc93ed06be9.jpg&h=2cf01b24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n潘九堂指手機公司老闆或產品經理，如果宣稱不試用 Apple、Samsung 產品，不是虛偽就是不稱職，或不關心產品或遠離一線。他暗示科技創新和進步是透過互相參考，而不是大家均在屋內或寺廟各自頓悟。潘九堂又轉發了另一網民的微博，表示華為的任正非使用 iPhone，前魅族 CEO 李楠離職後馬上換 iPhone，剛離開 OPPO 的行銷總裁沈義人亦以 iPhone 作為主力手機，表示事實證明 iPhone 依舊是最好的智能手機，認為雷軍抱著研究學習心態使用 iPhone 並無不妥。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2020-05/13/215827/uniqlo_1_de5b1cb80b09e41a9f980206af77367f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2020-05%2F13%2F215827%2Funiqlo_1_de5b1cb80b09e41a9f980206af77367f.jpg&h=5a0ce554&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4568/215827/1/1/130259/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4568%2F215827%2F1%2F1%2F130259%2F&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BedFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=32d702d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4568/215827/1/1/130259/</a>"},{"pid":"0a83b1e799ceb183dff6ebfbdc69ddf4e9857e08","tid":2019692,"uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ee8f7b1f6febccda4b3d5a733188e2f6e91e8a","tid":2019692,"uid":78662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249cb711cfab36154c118d73e431edb794017e64","tid":2019692,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2a04c4acca6e53566c32d185f7ef70ee028b25","tid":2019692,"uid":73565,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:21:16.000Z","msg":"小紅軍 全軍出擊！！！"},{"pid":"2f807f0b9955e775327aca6874257cb4e9a602d3","tid":2019692,"uid":47492,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:24:00.000Z","msg":"胡錫進孟晚舟表示讚好"},{"pid":"edabb4c520934e3639266ac80b15462c04050f38","tid":2019692,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8951ae4b6d786d924e5efd9daeec7f346a5c49b","tid":2019692,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2f807f0b9955e775327aca6874257cb4e9a602d3","tid":2019692,"uid":47492,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"rep